      *              * Preparazione pathname per file completato       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione nome file completo             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-det-pth-fso-pt2      .
           string    "/ZFAX/"    delimited by   size
                     w-det-pth-fso-nam
                                delimited by   spaces
                     ".SUB"     delimited by   size
                                          into w-det-pth-fso-pt2      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Pathname completo sotto /abd/asc            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "AS"                 to   s-ope                  .
           move      w-det-pth-fso-pt2    to   s-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
           move      s-pat                to   w-det-pth-fso-pt2      .
       det-pth-fso-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Routine di Bufferizzazione del testo della circolare      *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       buf-tst-cir-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione contatore righe                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-buf-tst-cir-ctr      .
       buf-tst-cir-050.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione pathname per il file contenente il *
      *              * testo                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test preliminare sul codice lingua          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        srt-cod-lng          not  = "I  " and
                     srt-cod-lng          not  = "ING"
                     move  "I  "          to   srt-cod-lng            .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione nome file completo             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-det-pth-fso-pt3      .
           string    "/ZFAX/"    delimited by   size
                     srt-cod-lng
                                delimited by   spaces
                     ".TXT"     delimited by   size
                                          into w-det-pth-fso-pt3      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Pathname completo sotto /abd/asc            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "AS"                 to   s-ope                  .
           move      w-det-pth-fso-pt3    to   s-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
           move      s-pat                to   w-det-pth-fso-pt3      .
       buf-tst-cir-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Apertura del file in input contenente il testo  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "OI"                 to   g-ope                  .
           move      "testo"              to   g-nam                  .
           move      w-det-pth-fso-pt3    to   g-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mcvinp"
                                         using g                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se errori                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        g-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to buf-tst-cir-900.
       buf-tst-cir-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ciclo di lettura file                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Lettura linea                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "GN"                 to   g-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mcvinp"
                                         using g                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se at-end                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        g-sts                =    e-end-fil
                     go to buf-tst-cir-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Incremento contatore righe                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-buf-tst-cir-ctr      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test sul numero massimo di righe            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-buf-tst-cir-ctr    >    w-buf-tst-cir-max
                     go to  buf-tst-cir-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Bufferizzazione riga di testo               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      g-rec                to   w-buf-tst-cir-rig
                                              (w-buf-tst-cir-ctr)     .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Aggiornamento contatore righe effettive     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-buf-tst-cir-ctr    to   w-buf-tst-cir-eff      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo a lettura                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     buf-tst-cir-200.
       buf-tst-cir-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Chiusura del file in input                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "CL"                 to   g-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mcvinp"
                                         using g                      .
       buf-tst-cir-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Subroutines per allineamenti a destra o a sinistra oppure *
      *    * al centro di campi alfanumerici di varia lunghezza, fi-   *
      *    * no ad un massimo di 240 caratteri, oppure per il conca-   *
      *    * tenamento, con o senza separazione, di max 10 substrin-   *
      *    * ghe in una unica substringa                               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           copy      "swd/std/prg/cpy/wallstr0.cps"                   .

